query:
SELECT la.labelCode, la.batch, la.expiryDate, la.quantity, p.sku, p.description, wl.code as locationCode
FROM labelAssociations la
INNER JOIN products p ON la.productId = p.id
INNER JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON la.locationId = wl.id
WHERE la.productId IN (
  SELECT DISTINCT productId FROM pickingWaveItems WHERE waveId = 1
)
LIMIT 20;
